                      00001 ; source code for Control Line system displays
                      00002 ;    Displays all have same code and use id switches on start up to set location
                      00003 ;       There are 3 displays, each has 8 digits (board no's)
                      00004 ;Pulse timing assumes xtal at 3.579 MHz   ///4.00Mhz
                      00005 
                      00006 ;History
                      00007 ;
