                      00010 ;18/8 call to test_count on start displayed 0 - 8 OK (once h/w issues fixed)
                      00011 ;23/8 Set ID, display correct digit on start Ok.
                      00012 ;   Decode of 422 data in OK.  
                      00013 ;18/10 Changed data monitor to TMR1. Tested in debug, data fail at 4.8 secs
                      00014 ;20/10 tested data fail and fixed display dim OK
                      00015 ;TEMP stopped clear display at end of test_count
                      00016 ;    
                      00017 ;TO DO
